# 1. FORCE WWW & HTTPS (Domain Consolidation)
# This stops you from having split traffic between "http" and "https"
http://itassetsolutions.com/* https://www.itassetsolutions.com/:splat  301!
https://itassetsolutions.com/* https://www.itassetsolutions.com/:splat  301!

# 2. FIX OLD BROKEN LINKS (301 Permanent Redirects)
# Even though we added routes to App.tsx, these server-side redirects are faster
# and better for Google SEO. They tell Google "This page has permanently moved."

# Disposition -> Enterprise ITAD
/services/it-asset-disposition   /services/enterprise-itad  301
/services/it-asset-management    /services/enterprise-itad  301
/services/e-waste-recycling      /services/enterprise-itad  301

# Recycling -> Value Recovery
/services/hardware-recycling     /services/it-asset-value-recovery  301

# Destruction -> Secure Data Destruction
/services/data-destruction       /services/secure-data-destruction  301
/services/secure-data-wiping     /services/secure-data-destruction  301
/services/hard-drive-shredding   /services/secure-data-destruction  301

# 3. SINGLE PAGE APP (SPA) FALLBACK
# This is the most critical line. It tells Netlify:
# "If the user asks for a page I don't know, send them to index.html and let React handle it."
/* /index.html  200